.howitworks
  .container
    .row.top-buffer
      .col-md-4
        h3.text-center Tell me your dream
        .thumbnail
          img(src="/img/howitworks/brainstorm.png")
        p Reach out to us with your ideas. Let us talk about what that special card looks like for you.

      .col-md-4
        h3.text-center Visualize Ideas
        .thumbnail
          img(src="/img/howitworks/design.png")
        p Then comes the design phase when the invitation card comes alive. Don't worry, you will have ample time to iterate on the design if it does not suit your needs.

      .col-md-4
        h3.text-center Invite Loved Ones
        .thumbnail
          img(src="/img/howitworks/share.png")
        p Thats it ! Yes, it is now time for you to share the invite on social media, email or distributed printed  copies to loved ones.
